title: Colorful Marine Sponge
description: A vibrant marine sponge with a unique, textured surface. The sponge is predominantly purple with a honeycomb-like pattern, featuring protruding spikes at the top. In the background, there are green coral formations, creating a colorful underwater scene.

title: Cross-section of a Coral Polyp
description: The image depicts a cross-section of a coral polyp, showcasing its internal structure. The polyp has a cylindrical shape with a central mouth surrounded by tentacles. The walls of the polyp are textured, indicating the presence of coral tissue. Arrows are used to illustrate the flow of water or nutrients, indicating the polyp's feeding mechanism and interaction with its environment.

title: Geometric Shape
description: A simple geometric outline of a rectangle with a small line extending from the bottom left corner.

title: Coral Reef Structure
description: A vibrant underwater scene featuring a large, purple coral structure resembling a sponge. The coral has a textured surface with intricate patterns and is surrounded by various marine life and colorful corals, set against a deep blue ocean backdrop.

title: Red Sea Sponge
description: A vibrant red sea sponge with multiple openings, set against a colorful coral reef background. The sponge has a textured surface and is surrounded by various marine life and corals.
